#

Blue Cheese and Pear Flatbread

25 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

AppetizerSnack

Tags:

EasyQuickSavoryAppetizer

Description

A delightful flatbread topped with creamy blue cheese, sweet pears, and a drizzle of honey for a perfect balance of flavors.

Ingredients

  • flatbread: 1 large
  • blue cheese: 4 oz
  • pear: 1 medium, thinly sliced
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • honey: 1 tbsp
  • walnuts: 1/4 cup, chopped (optional)
  • fresh arugula: 1 cup (optional)
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
